 very well describe the observed strongly\nsub-Lorentzian behavior in the 500-600 cm$^{-1}$ region. These experimental\nresults open renewed perspectives for studies of the past climate of Mars and\nextrasolar analogues.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 May 2018 16:12:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Nov 2018 05:53:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-05"}
