r more massive planets/brown\ndwarfs, and the core-accretion scenario is highly favoured, and high\nmetallicity is a prerequisite for massive planets to form.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 May 2018 19:53:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-09"}
