oposed methodology is scalable to generate\narbitrary sized microstructures, and it can serve as a pre-trained model to\nimprove the performance of a structure-property predictive model via transfer\nlearning.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 00:59:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Jan 2019 03:06:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-07"}
