shallower high-frequency behavior. The latter is well fit by a\nsingle power law with index in the range $-1.5$ to $-1.0$. A hybrid model is\nlikely needed to fully capture both the low-frequency and high-frequency\nbehavior of the temporal variations of atmospheric seeing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 05:52:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-31"}
