l\nflow ConvNet stream removed, the ablated WMR ConvNet nevertheless outperforms\ncompeting algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 07:57:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-09"}
